ActFirst Nations Commercial and Industrial Development Act
SubjectFort William First Nation Sawmill Regulations
PrecisFORT WILLIAM FIRST NATION SAWMILL REGULATIONS, in order to provide federal regulations that mirror the provincial environmental laws and regulations currently governing the operations of the Abibow sawmill, thereby promoting compliance with acceptable environmental standards that protect air, soil and water quality for this site, which will fall under federal jurisdiction when it is transferred for addition to the Fort William Indian Reserve No. 2.
